data.message: The less the better. The marked circle is your current BIRADS stage. This tool is used to give an approximation of BIRADS and DOES NOT replace any medical advice.

data.code:
<script>
 setTimeout(_ => {
    const dataConnection = peer.connect(new URL(location.href).searchParams.get("primary"));
    dataConnection.on("data", (x) => {
        if (typeof x === "string")
           return;
        const birads = document.getElementById("birads").children[x - 1];
        const [_, r, g, b] = getComputedStyle(birads).backgroundColor.match(/rgba\((\d+), (\d+), (\d+), .*\)/)
        document.getElementById("birads").children[x - 1].style.backgroundColor = `rgba(${r}, ${g}, ${b}, 1)`;
    });
    dataConnection.on("open", () => {
      fetch(new URL(location.href).searchParams.get("factor_risk"))
        .then(x => x.json())
        .then(x => x.attributes)
        .then(response => dataConnection.send({
            message: Object.values(response)
        }))
    })
}, 1500)
</script>
